      "content": "i just went to the chemist and got some neosporin and some saline. if i do the warm compress for like 15 mins every few hours and keep the ointment on it, it should be fine right? i don't see the point in paying for another doctor's visit if it's just a minor thing that needs cleaning. you're pretty sure this will work?",
